https://unity3d.com/legal/privacy-policy
Vungle
https://vungle.com/privacy/
Analytic & Attribution Companies:
These companies provide us with tools that inform us of how users interact with our Services; this allows us to improve these Services to meet your expectations. Generally, analytic & attribution companies collect data via their own SDKs. Such analytic & attribution companies, as well as their privacy policies can be found below:
Ad Partner
Privacy Policy
